<|channel>thought
<channel|># 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資或者做生意嘅時候，喺損失仲未擴大之前，決定賣出或者停止虧損嘅行為（量詞：次、招）
eng:to cut one's losses
<eg>
yue:個市跌得咁犀利，我諗住止蝕離場，唔好再輸落去。 (go3 si5 dit3 dak1 gam3 sai1 lei5, ngo5 nam2 zyu6 zi2 sik6 lei4 coeng4, m4 hou2 zoi3 soeng1 syu1 lok6 heoi3.)
eng:The market is dropping so sharply, I'm thinking of cutting my losses and leaving so I don't lose any more. [end of text]


